<headline>Special Weather Statement issued April 28 at 3:49AM EDT  by NWS Albany</headline>
<description>...ELEVATED FIRE WEATHER CONCERNS TODAY FOR NORTHWESTERN
CONNECTICUT...
A very dry airmass will combine with gusty northwest winds,
resulting in elevated fire weather concerns today. Northwest
winds 15 to 20 mph with gusts to 30 mph are expected, with
minimum relative humidities between 20 to 25 percent.</description>
